s at the end.", "tokens": [51268, 293, 22364, 264, 3542, 412, 264, 917, 13, 51372], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.19934791879555613, "compression_ratio": 1.5981308411214954, "no_speech_prob": 0.10401521623134613}, {"id": 51, "seek": 16264, "start": 182.79999999999998, "end": 186.48, "text": " Thanks to this, the processing becomes easy and fast.", "tokens": [51372, 2561, 281, 341, 11, 264, 9007, 3643, 1858, 293, 2370, 13, 51556], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.19934791879555613, "compression_ratio": 1.5981308411214954, "no_speech_prob": 0.10401521623134613}, {"id": 52, "seek": 16264, "start": 186.48, "end": 188.79999999999998, "text": " This is known as parallel processing.", "tokens": [51556, 639, 307, 2570, 382, 8952, 9007, 13, 51672], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.19934791879555613, "compression_ratio": 1.5981308411214954, "no_speech_prob": 0.10401521623134613}, {"id": 53, "seek": 18880, "start": 189.12, "end": 193.36, "text": " Now that we have stored and processed our big data,", "tokens": [50380, 823, 300, 321, 362, 12187, 293, 18846, 527, 955, 1412, 11, 50592], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1439594268798828, "compression_ratio": 1.6147540983606556, "no_speech_prob": 0.12867571413516998}, {"id": 54, "seek": 18880, "start": 193.36, "end": 196.88000000000002, "text": " we can analyze this data for numerous applications,", "tokens": [50592, 321, 393, 12477, 341, 1412, 337, 12546, 5821, 11, 50768], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1439594268798828, "compression_ratio": 1.6147540983606556, "no_speech_prob": 0.12867571413516998}, {"id": 55, "seek": 18880, "start": 196.88000000000002, "end": 199.92000000000002, "text": " in games like Halo 3 and Call of Duty,", "tokens": [50768, 294, 2813, 411, 29795, 805, 293, 7807, 295, 33045, 11, 50920], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1439594268798828, "compression_ratio": 1.6147540983606556, "no_speech_prob": 0.12867571413516998}, {"id": 56, "seek": 18880, "start": 199.92000000000002, "end": 202.24, "text": " designers analyze user data,", "tokens": [50920, 16196, 12477, 4195, 1412, 11, 51036], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1439594268798828, "compression_ratio": 1.6147540983606556, "no_speech_prob": 0.12867571413516998}, {"id": 57, "seek": 18880, "start": 202.24, "end": 205.76000000000002, "text": " to understand at which stage most of the users pause,", "tokens": [51036, 281, 1223, 412, 597, 3233, 881, 295, 264, 5022, 10465, 11, 51212], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1439594268798828, "compression_ratio": 1.6147540983606556, "no_speech_prob": 0.12867571413516998}, {"id": 58, "seek": 18880, "start": 205.76000000000002, "end": 207.92000000000002, "text": " restart, or quit playing.", "tokens": [51212, 21022, 11, 420, 10366, 2433, 13, 51320], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1439594268798828, "compression_ratio": 1.6147540983606556, "no_speech_prob": 0.12867571413516998}, {"id": 59, "seek": 18880, "start": 207.92000000000002, "end": 211.12, "text": " This insight can help them rework on the storyline of the game", "tokens": [51320, 639, 11269, 393, 854, 552, 48376, 322, 264, 30828, 295, 264, 1216, 51480], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1439594268798828, "compression_ratio": 1.6147540983606556, "no_speech_prob": 0.12867571413516998}, {"id": 60, "seek": 18880, "start": 211.12, "end": 213.44, "text": " and improve the user experience,", "tokens": [51480, 293, 3470, 264, 4195, 1752, 11, 51596], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1439594268798828, "compression_ratio": 1.6147540983606556, "no_speech_prob": 0.12867571413516998}, {"id": 61, "seek": 18880, "start": 213.44, "end": 215.92000000000002, "text": " which in turn reduces the customer churn rate.", "tokens": [51596, 597, 294, 1261, 18081, 264, 5474, 417, 925, 3314, 13, 51720], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1439594268798828, "compression_ratio": 1.6147540983606556, "no_speech_prob": 0.12867571413516998}, {"id": 62, "seek": 21592, "start": 216.79999999999998, "end"