: 21592, "start": 233.2, "end": 235.35999999999999, "text": " which wasn't possible earlier.", "tokens": [51228, 597, 2067, 380, 1944, 3071, 13, 51336], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09760994381374782, "compression_ratio": 1.57679180887372, "no_speech_prob": 0.049965810030698776}, {"id": 69, "seek": 21592, "start": 235.35999999999999, "end": 237.2, "text": " These are some of the clear indications", "tokens": [51336, 1981, 366, 512, 295, 264, 1850, 44450, 51428], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09760994381374782, "compression_ratio": 1.57679180887372, "no_speech_prob": 0.049965810030698776}, {"id": 70, "seek": 21592, "start": 237.2, "end": 239.35999999999999, "text": " of how valuable big data can be,", "tokens": [51428, 295, 577, 8263, 955, 1412, 393, 312, 11, 51536], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09760994381374782, "compression_ratio": 1.57679180887372, "no_speech_prob": 0.049965810030698776}, {"id": 71, "seek": 21592, "start": 239.35999999999999, "end": 242.16, "text": " once it is accurately processed and analyzed.", "tokens": [51536, 1564, 309, 307, 20095, 18846, 293, 28181, 13, 51676], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09760994381374782, "compression_ratio": 1.57679180887372, "no_speech_prob": 0.049965810030698776}, {"id": 72, "seek": 21592, "start": 242.79999999999998, "end": 244.48, "text": " So, here's a question for you.", "tokens": [51708, 407, 11, 510, 311, 257, 1168, 337, 291, 13, 51792], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09760994381374782, "compression_ratio": 1.57679180887372, "no_speech_prob": 0.049965810030698776}, {"id": 73, "seek": 24448, "start": 244.56, "end": 246.88, "text": " Which of the following statements is not correct", "tokens": [50368, 3013, 295, 264, 3480, 12363, 307, 406, 3006, 50484], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1550975262540058, "compression_ratio": 1.5854700854700854, "no_speech_prob": 0.015614785254001617}, {"id": 74, "seek": 24448, "start": 246.88, "end": 250.56, "text": " about Hadoop Dis